# Deni Architecture

## Overview
Deni is a community driven event and food truck discovery app focused on trust, verification, and accuracy.

## Core Goals
- Reduce spam and fake events
- Promote trusted organizers
- Enable community verification
- Provide real time, location aware events

## High Level Components
- Mobile App (React Native)
- Backend API
- Database
- Trust and Verification System

## Event Lifecycle
1. User signs up and logs in
2. Event is created in draft state
3. Verification signals are collected
4. Trust score is calculated
5. Event is published when confidence meets policy
6. Event visibility adjusts over time

## Backend Services
- Event Service
- Verification Service
- Trust Scoring Service
- Reputation Service
- Moderation Service (optional)
- Notification Service
